N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4830.2 - Proceedings respecting licenses issued pursuant to Bingo Licensing Law

State Regulations

Proceedings to revoke a license issued pursuant to the

Bingo Licensing Law may be instituted either by the municipal governing body or
by the commission, on the initiative of either or on complaint of any person, including any public official or agency. Notes
